The **~WikiPoll** [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] provides configurable polls.

== Usage ==

{{{
<<WikiPoll arguments
    questions and possible answers
>>
}}}

Syntax:
{{{
question[1]="Do you like PhpWiki?"
answer[1][1]="Yes" answer[1][2]="Do not know" answer[1][3]="No"
}}}

Administration:
{{{
<<WikiPoll page=PhpWikiPoll admin=1>>
}}}
and protect this page properly (e.g. ~PhpWikiPoll/Admin)

== Arguments ==

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| **require_all**
| 1 if all questions must be answered
| 1
|-
| **require_least**
| How many at least
| 0
|}

== Example ==

See example in [[PhpWikiPoll]].

